pageProduct.name: Sukin Hydration Hydra Eye Gel 15ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Seriously Hydrate The Delicate Under Eye Area With Our Fragrance-Free Water Gel.

Warnings

Avoid Contact With Eyes. If Irritation Occurs Rinse Immediately And Discontinue Use. For External Use Only.

Common Uses

Seriously Hydrate The Delicate Under Eye Area With Our Fragrance-Free Water Gel. A Bio-Marine Blend Of Ocean Algae, Hyaluronic Acid & Blue Maize Extract Will Deeply Rehydrate To Leave Your Skin Looking Dewy And Bright For Over 72 Hours.

Ingredients

Water (Aqua), Glycerin, Saccharide Isomerate (Maize Complex), Sodium Hyaluronate, Ascophyllum Nodosum Extract (Kelp), Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Root Extract, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Leaf Extract, Leuconostoc/Radish Root Ferment Filtrate, Amorphophallus Konjac Root Extract, Cellulose Gum, Carrageenan, Citric Acid, Sodium Citrate, Sodium Chloride, Ethylhexylglycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Benzyl Alcohol.

Directions

After Cleansing In The Morning, Gently Massage Into Face, Neck And Décolletage.
